## Included

| Endpoint | Method | Used by | Purpose | Blast |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `{{endpoint_1}}` | {{method_1}} | {{agent_1}} | {{purpose_1}} | L{{blast_1}} |
| `{{endpoint_2}}` | {{method_2}} | {{agent_2}} | {{purpose_2}} | L{{blast_2}} |
| `{{endpoint_3}}` | {{method_3}} | {{agent_3}} | {{purpose_3}} | L{{blast_3}} |

Blast levels: L1 read-only / L2 write-scoped / L3 write-unrestricted /
L4 send-external per `governance/blast-radius.md`. Approval gating
required for L3+ on `semi`/`supervised` agents.

## Excluded (least-privilege)

These endpoints exist in the vendor's API but are NOT in this wrapper:

| Endpoint | Method | Reason for exclusion |
|---|---|---|
| `{{excluded_endpoint_1}}` | {{method}} | {{rationale_1}} |
| `{{excluded_endpoint_2}}` | {{method}} | {{rationale_2}} |
| `/v1/admin/*` | * | No agent needs admin scope; concentrating risk |
| `* DELETE` | DELETE | No agent needs delete; high blast radius |

If a future agent needs an excluded endpoint, the team revisits Phase 3
inventory protocol and either expands this subset or declines the
agent's blast-radius escalation.

