## Webhook hand-off (if applicable)

If the vendor pushes events for some operations, the wrapper does NOT
handle inbound webhooks — that's a separate `NEEDS-WEBHOOK` tier
artifact. See `integrations/needs-webhook/` for the receiver spec.

